moduleMetadataJson.name: Applocker Evasion - Microsoft .NET Assembly Registration Utility
moduleMetadataJson.description:
This module will assist you in evading Microsoft
         Windows Applocker and Software Restriction Policies.
         This technique utilises the Microsoft signed binaries
         RegAsm.exe or RegSvcs.exe to execute user supplied code.
author: Nick Tyrer <@NickTyrer>
Casey Smith

options.name: WORKSPACE
options.description: Specify the workspace for this module

options.name: TXT_FILE
options.description: Filename for the evasive file (default: regasm_regsvcs.txt)
